loop are of two types:
1. entry controlled:while,for
2.exit controlled:do ..while 

loop 3 parts:
initilization part 
condition
increment/decrement

initilization ;i=1
while(i<=10){
    //body part
  i++;
}
for(initilization;condition;incre/decre){
    //body of loop;
}
initilization
do{
    //body
    incre/decre
}while(condition)